---
title: Glazed Beef Meatballs & Kumara Wedges with Cucumber Salad & Mayonnaise
description: Oh, happy days! With a heavenly combination of a crisp green salad, served alongside kumara wedges and a sticky-sweet cherry glaze slathered over beef meatballs, this is a modern and delicious union that will be happily devoured by all.

*We’ve replaced the tomato in this recipe with cherry
tomatoes due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
